23
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,919
and your teammates

24
00:01:19,319 --> 00:01:20,480
think of you?

25
00:01:20,599 --> 00:01:22,120
Will they still treat you as a teammate?

26
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:28,992
Take this.

27
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,720
You told me

28
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:36,480
