29
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:40,239
Today, let's take a clear one.

30
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:42,959
Let go of me.

31
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:48,120
Do it. Why are you hesitating?

32
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,680
With those pictures in my hand,

33
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:52,839
