41
00:02:20,119 --> 00:02:21,199
I've already called the police.

42
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:23,000
Go! The police will be here soon.

43
00:02:23,616 --> 00:02:24,919
Get lost!

44
00:02:24,919 --> 00:02:26,752
Xu Nannan.

45
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:31,264
Are you okay?

46
00:02:31,839 --> 00:02:34,720
Xu Nannan, you will regret this.

47
00:02:39,679 --> 00:02:41,880
Wait for my big gift.

48
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,520
Xu Nannan, you'll see.

49
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,119
Han Xizhou.

50
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:21,919
You're awake. Are you okay?

51
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,279
Do you feel uncomfortable anywhere?

52
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,279
